    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "9b6fb828_7e5f0dc7",
        "filename": "golden/modules/common.js",
        "patchSetId": 1
      },
      "lineNbr": 29,
      "author": {
        "id": 10009
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-03-30T06:58:34Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "IIUC this approach forces all digest and diff images used by various demo pages to be served from the same /dist path.\n\nIt would be cleaner if we could specify a path specific to a particular demo page, such as /dist/image-compare-sk. This would allow us to store demo assets in component-specific directories under //golden/demo-page-assets instead of lumping them all together under the same directory.\n\nHow about this:\n- Let\u0027s introduce a digestAndDiffImagePathPrefix variable, empty by default, and a function setDigestAndDiffImagePathPrefix to override said variable from demo pages.\n- When digestAndDiffImagePathPrefix is empty, the imgSrc and diffImgSrc helpers should return the default paths, e.g. \"/img/images/XXX.png\", \"/img/diffs/XXX-YYY.png\", etc.\n- When digestAndDiffImagePathPrefix is set, said helpers should return a path prefixed by digestAndDiffImagePathPrefix, e.g. \"/dist/image-compare-sk/XXX.png\". \"/dist/image-compare-sk/XXX-YYY.png\", etc.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 29,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 29,
        "endChar": 3
      },
      "revId": "2973f8c941dc8aec90e031600466e954616faba7",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "2b756825_11dcb731",
        "filename": "golden/modules/common.js",
        "patchSetId": 1
      },
      "lineNbr": 29,
      "author": {
        "id": 5395
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-03-30T12:10:57Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I see keeping all demo pages using the same /dist path as a feature, not a bug. Very few components actually serve the images directly, so there\u0027s no need for the extra complexity.",
      "parentUuid": "9b6fb828_7e5f0dc7",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 29,
        "startChar": 0,
